fwprop.note:
Start Action for Command (12,5) to add one or more parameter monitor (PMON) definitions. 
The command carries a list of parameter monitor definitions to be added to the PMDL
(Parameter Monitoring Definition List). The index i iterates over all the PMONs in the command.

fwprop.note:
This procedure generates a (1,4) report for each rejected parameter monitor
definition in the command. The (1,4) reports are generated by the Command
Verification Failure Procedure. The start action is declared successful as long 
as at least one valid parameter monitor definition is accepted for execution.
